description:
This is a 17 minute workout called 'Chair Yoga | Yoga With Adriene' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Chair Yoga invites you to find mobility in a way that is soft and gentle but also really supportive and beneficial. This 17 minute practice invites awareness and integrity into the body, specifically the line of the spine. Activate the muscles that help you find length up through the spine for better posture and energy flow. Great Yoga For Seniors as well!

Share with a friend and let me know how it goes do. Chair Yoga invites you to find mobility that can be soft and gentle but also really supportive, strengthening, stabilizing and beneficial. This 17 minute practice invites awareness and integrity into the body, specifically the line of the spine. Activate the muscles that help you find length up through the spine for better posture and energy flow. Great Yoga For Seniors as well!
